  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MiMo-V2-Flash</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2518518518518518\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"292\" data-imgfileid=\"100017290\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=696017fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwF5s30VicOLwAZ6kpDo51FuXHhyQzuono21zG9zFTvZN9hgwWwudYD1geV4o37BxWia5phGm8YORzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MiMo-V2-Flash是一个拥有 3090 亿总参数和 150 亿活跃参数的多专家（MoE）语言模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型专为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">高速推理</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">智能工作流</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">设计，采用新颖的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">混合注意力架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多令牌预测（MTP）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">技术，实现了最先进的性能，同时显著降低了推理成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mimo-v2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mimo-v2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：SAM-Audio</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3574074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"414\" data-imgfileid=\"100017294\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c4770005&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwF5s30VicOLwAZ6kpDo51Fum7yxbM6f6DzTlLZibeM43KSGpyhGqo23cFkuIqKIp4K9Vn33ibicNFbSA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★SAM-Audio是一个基础模型，旨在通过文本、视觉或时间提示隔离音频中的任何声音。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型能够根据自然语言描述、视频中的视觉线索或时间跨度，从复杂的音频混合中分离出特定的声音。项目提供了运行推理的代码、下载训练模型检查点的链接以及如何使用模型的示例笔记本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sam-audio\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sam-audio</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Nanbeige4-Base</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.600925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"698\" data-imgfileid=\"100017292\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ade64c04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwF5s30VicOLwAZ6kpDo51FutvtHQ5WqNllHRQpGQBAOh0dOHMJXsjC1sJJ2HopFX1aJyLkjCmbW8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Nanbeige4-Base是第四代 Nanbeige LLM 家族中的一个基础模型，拥有30亿参数。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过持续改进数据质量和训练方法，该模型展示了即使是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">紧凑</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的模型也能实现先进的性能。在相同的训练数据上进行监督微调时，该模型显著优于同尺寸的开源模型，甚至超越了更大的模型如 Qwen3-8B。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanbeige4-3b-base\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanbeige4-3b-base</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：Fun-ASR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.33240740740740743\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"386\" data-imgfileid=\"100017291\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=23f1fdb5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwF5s30VicOLwAZ6kpDo51FuPfoUC7Efa4FRnbhMEayoD8Mwyib2o1L6uhhx5fJ9NfPEkYJ2AC2X67g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Fun-ASR是由同义实验室推出的端到端语音识别大型模型。该模型经过数千万小时的真实语音数据训练，具备强大的语境理解能力和行业适应性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Fun-ASR支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">低延迟</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的实时转录，覆盖31种语言，尤其在教育和金融等垂直领域表现出色，能够准确识别</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">专业术语</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">行业表达</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，有效解决</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">“幻觉”生成</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">语言混淆</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">等问题，实现“听得清、懂得意、写得准”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fun-asr\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fun-asr</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：SenseNova-SI</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"100017296\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b066f84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwF5s30VicOLwAZ6kpDo51FuVqoh67q7dpQKTn9XticIIRmOMu8cLicR1AY3qmDzolNFvz8H3hja3fpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★SenseNova-SI项目旨在通过多模态基础模型提升空间智能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目基于现有的多模态基础模型，如Qwen3-VL和InternVL3，以及统一的理解和生成模型Bagel，构建了SenseNova-SI家族。通过系统地策划SenseNova-SI-8M，项目收集了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">八百万个多样化的数据样本</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，展示了在多个空间智能基准测试中的卓越表现。项目还分析了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">数据扩展</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的影响，讨论了多样化数据训练所带来的早期泛化能力，并验证了潜在的下游应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sensenova-si\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sensenova-si</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：LoFA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"434\" data-imgfileid=\"100017295\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2598432f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwF5s30VicOLwAZ6kpDo51FuIQGIVx5vUpnPn80DQOmftbAPeJQtEkUhdZzAaRPMERIZJVHAV0ogfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LoFA项目旨在通过预测个性化先验来实现视觉生成模型的快速适应。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目的官方实现提供了一种新颖的方法，能够在视觉生成任务中快速调整模型以适应个性化需求。这种方法在保持生成质量的同时，显著减少了适应时间。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lofa\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lofa</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了小米开源的 MiMo-V2-Flash 等多款最新 AI 模型和框架，涵盖大模型、音频、语音、多模态以及视觉生成等领域。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了小米开源的 MiMo-V2-Flash 等多款最新 AI 模型和框架，涵盖大模型、音频、语音、多模态以及视觉生成等领域。",
  "summary": "文章以“今日开源”的形式，快速介绍了多款在特定领域具有代表性的 AI 模型和框架。小米开源的 MiMo-V2-Flash 作为新一代 MoE 语言模型，通过多令牌预测技术在高性能与低推理成本间取得平衡。SAM-Audio 专注于复杂的音频分离任务。Nanbeige4-Base 则展示了紧凑型模型通过优化数据和训练方法，其性能可超越大型模型。Fun-ASR 提供强大的端到端语音识别能力，并有效解决行业痛点。此外，SenseNova-SI 旨在通过多模态基础模型提升空间智能，LoFA 用于视觉生成模型的快速个性化适应。文章旨在为读者提供最新的 AI 技术开源动态，特别是突出开源 AI 模型在效率和性能上的突破。",
  "mainPoints": [
